# Hylo.com shared modules

Put all source files in `src/` and is built to `dist/`. After making your changes to files in `src/`, run `npm run build` to transpile to ES5, test, check everthing in, run `npm version <patch|minor|major>` and then `npm publish`. This should be published to the `hylodevs` npm account.

Next steps:

- Use microbundle once a viable multiple entry-points config becomes available: https://github.com/developit/microbundle/issues/50
